Braided Upstyle Tutorial🌸

I used @designmehair PUFF.ME • VOLUMIZING POWDER on braids before expanding and pulling them up. I set the style with HOLD.ME • THREE-WAY HAIRSPRAY on level Medium. This spray provides 3 levels of hold: light, medium, high hold in 1 can. All you have to do is twist the nozzle to the desired hold, shake well and spray on dry hair.
